data.title: About: The County Fair (1934 film)
data.meta_description: The County Fair, also called The Country Fair in some reissues, is a short animated film distributed by Universal Pictures, in the Oswald the Lucky Rabbit series. The cartoon shares a very similar title with Kounty Fair, another Oswald short released four years prior.
